'''2020年世界公路自行车锦标赛'''是第93届[[世界公路自行车锦标赛|世界公路自行车锦标赛]]，于2020年9月24日至27日在意大利伊莫拉举办。此次比赛原计划在[[瑞士|瑞士]][[埃格勒|埃格勒]]和[[马蒂尼_(瓦莱州)|马蒂尼]]进行，然而受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影响，瑞士升级防疫措施，放弃了该届比赛的主办权。国际自行车联合会之后宣布意大利伊莫拉获得主办权。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/53942004 |title=Road World Championships moved to Imola |work=[[BBC体育|BBC Sport]] |date=2020-09-02 |accessdate=2020-09-05 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929191348/https://www.bbc.com/sport/cycling/53942004 |archivedate=2020-09-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The 2020 UCI Road World Championships will take place in Imola and the Emilia-Romagna region (Italy) on a very challenging course|url=https://www.uci.org/news/2020/the-2020-uci-road-world-championships-will-take-place-in-imola-and-the-emilia-romagna-region-italy-on-a-very-challenging-course|work=Union Cycliste Internationale|date=2020-09-02|accessdate=2020-09-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903092838/https://www.uci.org/news/2020/the-2020-uci-road-world-championships-will-take-place-in-imola-and-the-emilia-romagna-region-italy-on-a-very-challenging-course|archivedate=2020-09-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此次比赛不设23岁以下组和青年组，尽管如此，23岁以下组的选手仍有资格参加精英组的比赛。<ref name="tech"/>

